profile_data.summary:
Data Science Professional with 3+ years of experience delivering impactful business insights across diverse industries, including Utilities, Finance, and Law in both US and UK markets. Expertise in AI, Machine Learning, Data Science, and Data Visualization, with a proven track record of deploying data-driven solutions to solve complex, real-world problems. 

My proficiencies are in creatively dissecting and understanding the types of stories and trends that lay hidden in data. My expertise lies in transforming complex datasets into strategic insights, fostering significant business developments, and contributing to growth for my previous employers.

My academic endeavors are complemented by hands-on experience in data engineering, ETL processes, and the adept use of machine learning techniques to address and solve real-world challenges. Moreover, I possess a strong command over data visualization and model deployment, proven during my tenure. My professional toolkit includes proficiency in programming languages such as Python, R, and SQL, alongside a robust understanding of databases and cloud platforms.


Programming and Tools: Python, SQL, R, PySpark, SAS, C++, ReactJS, Azure ML, Git, Visual Studio
Databases: MySQL, PostgreSQL, Microsoft SQL Server (T-SQL), PL/SQL, NoSQL (MongoDB)
Libraries: Tensorflow, Scikit-learn, Keras, Seaborn, Matplotlib, NLTK, sqldf, dplyr, Numpy, Pandas
Visualization Tools: PowerBI, Tableau, Google Analytics, Looker, Python Dash, Advanced Excel
Cloud: Microsoft Azure, AWS(EC2, DynamoDB, S3, Redshift), GCP
